metadata.name: Hyper-municipal Sigil Warfare I
metadata.description:
“Nothing is true, everything is permitted”


This piece is a continuation of my effort to extract something familiar from the unfamiliar, abstract geometry. City-like, circuit-like, "angels", cut-up and reassembled into patterns resembling some sigil magic(k) techniques. Fed through frayed wires and faulty transmitters. Ultimately, acting as a mirror. 

Fully generative geometry and post-processing, written in Clojurescript and WebGL, making use of techniques including raymarching, rectangle packing, and pixel feedback.
